```json
{
  "translations": [
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b1",
      "translation": "In the fourth quarter of 2020, we celebrated AIA's tenth anniversary of listing on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange. Looking back, AIA's IPO set multiple records and remains"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b2",
      "translation": "the largest insurance industry IPO globally. It has been a privilege to work alongside our Board members. AIA's"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b3",
      "translation": "business has continued to expand during this period, becoming the world's largest life insurance company by market capitalisation."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b5",
      "translation": "All non-executive directors on the Board are independent individuals with extensive governance and leadership experience in both public and private sectors. We work together"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b6",
      "translation": "with determination to maintain a corporate culture adhering to the highest international corporate governance standards. We firmly believe that deeply rooted corporate governance culture, combined with sound risk"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b7",
      "translation": "management framework, is the foundation for sustainable development of every institution."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b8",
      "translation": "One of the Board's key responsibilities is to ensure a strong pipeline of leadership talent and implement effective succession arrangements. We welcomed Mr. Lee Yuen Cheung on 1 June 2020"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b9",
      "translation": "to succeed the retiring Mr. Wong King Fai as Group Chief Executive Officer and President. On behalf of the Board, I wish to express deep appreciation to Mr. Lee Yuen Cheung and his management team"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b10",
      "translation": "for their outstanding management in navigating an unprecedented operating environment and driving our business forward. We also extend our heartfelt thanks to Mr. Wong King Fai"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b11",
      "translation": "for his years of excellent leadership and significant contributions to AIA."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b12",
      "translation": "Environmental, social and governance matters are increasingly important globally. We are committed to helping drive society towards a better future, and our environmental,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b13",
      "translation": "social and governance initiatives were again recognised in 2020. According to Sustainalytics' assessment, AIA ranked second among over 270 insurance companies,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b14",
      "translation": "demonstrating our excellent corporate governance strength and quality. We continued to receive the \"Prime\" Environmental, Social and Governance Corporate Rating from Institutional Shareholder Services"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b16",
      "translation": "We believe we need to take further steps to achieve better outcomes for our communities. This remains a priority for myself and the Board"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b18",
      "translation": "Today, customer demand for AIA's products, services and high-quality advice has never been stronger. Our strategy is built on Asia's strong structural growth"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b19",
      "translation": "drivers and supported by multiple factors, including unprecedented wealth creation, rapidly expanding protection gaps, evolving consumer preferences,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b20",
      "translation": "digital technology proliferation, and market focus on long-term sustainable development. The Board is confident AIA is well-positioned to capture the significant"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b21",
      "translation": "opportunities in the region, providing financial security to customers and their families when needed most, giving them peace of mind, while creating shared value for all stakeholders."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b22",
      "translation": "Finally, AIA's strong and sustained growth since listing is thanks to the trust of our customers and shareholders. On behalf of all Board members,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b23",
      "translation": "I wish to express our sincere gratitude for your continued support."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b24",
      "translation": "Tse Sze Wing"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b25",
      "translation": "Independent Non-Executive Chairman"
    }
  ]
}
```
